// Libraries
import React from 'react'
import { Route } from 'react-router'
import AccountDisabled from '../../../components/accountDisabled'
import MakePayment from '../../../components/accountDisabled/makePayment'
import PaymentDone from '../../../components/accountDisabled/paymentDone'
import AddNewPaymentMethod from '../addNewPaymentMethod'

function platformBlocked () {
  return (
    <Route>
      <Route path='/plataforma-bloqueada' component={AccountDisabled} />
      <Route
        path='/plataforma-bloqueada/realizar-pago'
        component={MakePayment}
      />
      <Route
        path='/plataforma-bloqueada/agregar-metodo-pago'
        component={AddNewPaymentMethod}
      />
      <Route
        path='/plataforma-bloqueada/pago-exitoso'
        component={PaymentDone}
      />
    </Route>
  )
}

export default platformBlocked
